<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
</head>

<body class="bg-navy font-sans text-ivory min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-20 flex-grow w-full">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-ivory tracking-tight mb-4">
                Seja um Parceiro <span class="text-gold">Auto Guincho</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Sua empresa merece destaque. Escolha o plano que melhor atende sua operação e comece a receber chamados qualificados hoje mesmo.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tabela de Planos -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-stretch">
            
            <!-- Plano Básico -->
            <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col hover:border-gray-700 transition lg:mt-8">
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-300 mb-2">Plano Básico</h3>
                    <div class="text-4xl font-black text-white">Grátis</div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Para quem está começando</p>
                </div>
                
                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 flex-grow">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        1 Categoria principal
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Atendimento em 1 Cidade
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Aparece ao final das buscas
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500 line-through">
                        Sem fotos ou galeria
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500 line-through">
                        Sem Mapa ou Redes Sociais
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <a href="https://wa.me/<%= WHATSAPP_CONTACT %>?text=Oi.%20Gostaria%20de%20atualizar%20os%20dados%20da%20minha%20empresa%20no%20Auto%20Guincho%20(Plano%20Básico)." 
                   class="w-full py-4 px-6 rounded-2xl font-bold text-center border border-gray-700 text-gray-300 hover:bg-white/5 transition">
                    Atualizar Dados Grátis
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Plano Intermediário -->
            <div class="bg-gray-900 border-2 border-slate-700 rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col relative scale-105 shadow-2xl z-10">
                <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-slate-700 text-white text-xs font-black px-4 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest">
                    Mais Popular
                </div>
                
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-300 mb-2">Intermediário</h3>
                    <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 text-white">
                        <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-500">R$</span>
                        <span class="text-5xl font-black">19,90</span>
                        <span class="text-gray-500">/mês*</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2">*No plano anual (R$ 238,80)</p>
                </div>
                
                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 flex-grow">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-ivory">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Categorias ilimitadas
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-ivory">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Atendimento em até 8 Cidades
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-ivory">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Galeria com até 3 fotos
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-ivory">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Destaque intermediário nas buscas
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600 line-through">
                        Sem Redes Sociais ou Mapas
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <a href="https://wa.me/<%= WHATSAPP_CONTACT %>?text=Oi.%20Quero%20ser%20Parceiro%20Auto%20Guincho%20com%20o%20Plano%20Intermediário." 
                   class="w-full py-4 px-6 rounded-2xl font-bold font-serif text-center bg-ivory text-navy hover:bg-white transition shadow-xl">
                    Assinar Agora
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Plano Elite -->
            <div class="bg-black/40 border border-gold/30 rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col hover:border-gold/50 transition lg:mt-8 shadow-gold/5 shadow-2xl">
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gold mb-2">Elite</h3>
                    <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 text-gold">
                        <span class="text-2xl font-bold opacity-60">R$</span>
                        <span class="text-5xl font-black">29,90</span>
                        <span class="text-gold/60">/mês*</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gold/40 mt-2">*No plano anual (R$ 358,80)</p>
                </div>
                
                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 flex-grow">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gold/80">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Máxima exposição (Topo das Buscas)
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gold/80">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Cidades e Categorias ILIMITADAS
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gold/80">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Galeria com até 10 fotos
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gold/80">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Google Maps e Redes Sociais
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gold/80">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                        Selo Ouro de Verificação
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <a href="https://wa.me/<%= WHATSAPP_CONTACT %>?text=Oi.%20Quero%20ser%20Parceiro%20Auto%20Guincho%20com%20o%20Plano%20ELITE." 
                   class="w-full py-4 px-6 rounded-2xl font-bold text-center bg-gold text-black hover:bg-yellow-400 transition shadow-lg shadow-gold/20">
                    Contratar Plano Elite
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Opções Extras -->
        <div class="mt-24 max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white/5 rounded-3xl p-10 border border-white/10 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 italic font-serif">Apoio ao Gestor do Perfil</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="text-left">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Encontrou sua empresa mas quer remover?</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Respeitamos a sua privacidade. Solicite a exclusão total da sua página gratuitamente.</p>
                    <a href="https://wa.me/<%= WHATSAPP_CONTACT %>?text=Oi.%20Vi%20minha%20empresa%20no%20Auto%20Guincho%20e%20gostaria%20de%20remover%20os%20dados." 
                       class="text-xs font-bold text-red-500 hover:text-red-400">Solicitar Exclusão de Dados</a>
                </div>
                <div class="text-left border-l border-white/10 pl-0 md:pl-8">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Precisa de ajuda com o painel?</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Se você já é parceiro e precisa de suporte técnico ou financeiro, fale diretamente conosco.</p>
                    <a href="https://wa.me/<%= WHATSAPP_CONTACT %>?text=Oi.%20Já%20sou%20parceiro%20do%20Auto%20Guincho%20e%20preciso%20de%20suporte." 
                       class="text-xs font-bold text-gold hover:text-yellow-400">Falar com Suporte Técnico</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>
